Impact
- Journal format | 5 | Constraint as strength | Narrative form becomes the novel's power
- Mystery structure | 5 | Perfect pacing | Reveals arrive at exactly the right weight
- The world itself | 5 | Most original | Setting unlike anything I have encountered
- The ending | 5 | Perfect and complete | Precisely as long as it needed to be

